products.title: ASUS TUF Gaming GeForce GTX 1650 Super Overclocked 4GB Edition HDMI DP DVI Gaming Graphics Card (TUF-GTX1650S-O4G-GAMING)
features: Powered by NVIDIA Turing with 1800 MHz Boost Clock, 1280 CUDA cores and overclocked 4GB GDDR6 memory.
Space-grade lubricant brings the durability of dual Ball bearings to quieter Sleeve bearing designs.
Protective backplate secures components during transportation and installation.
Tuf compatibility testing runs cards through a suite of tests to ensure TUF Gaming motherboards, chassis, and other TUF Gaming Alliance components work together flawlessly
Auto-extreme technology delivers premium quality and reliability using an automated manufacturing process
products.description: Powered by NVIDIA Turing, the Asus TUF Gaming GeForce GTX 1650 Super delivers legendary durability and performance Featuring auto extreme manufacturing technology. The overclocked 4GB GDDR6 memory deliver over 50% more memory bandwidth for high-speed gaming to match Asus TUF Gaming motherboards and TUF Gaming Alliance products.
